name: Jennifer Yieri
description: I am loving caring and kind and I want to meet someone who is going to love me just for me. I’m honest, loyal, and when I have a man I’m faithful to him and treat him great. I’ve been single for the past 4 years because I broke up with my boy friend and took time to focus on my life. I don’t go out to bars and clubs, so I guess I just haven’t been going to places where I have the opportunity to meet men.
